Salesforce Summer ’24 Release Notes
What’s New for the Salesforce Release Notes?

Monthly Release Notes
Release Update: Analytics, Commerce, Customization, Data Cloud, Deployment, Development, Lightning Components, Visualforce, Apex, API, Packaging, Platform Development Tools, Salesforce CLI, Salesforce Extensions for Visual Studio Code

Get Started Faster on Salesforce Extensions for Visual Studio Code with the New Documentation Site
The new documentation site aggregates all the documentation in a site that’s easier to navigate. Requests to the old site redirect to the new site.

New and Changed Items for Developers: Einstein, Experience Cloud, Field Service, Industries, Marketing, MuleSoft, Mobile, OmniStudio, Revenue, Sales, Salesforce CMS, Salesforce Flow, Salesforce for Slack Integrations

Where: The new documentation site is available on developer.salesforce.com.
title: Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes
